6
00:00:24,900 --> 00:00:30,180
And yet, rogue planets might carry alien life to all corners of the galaxy.

7
00:00:30,180 --> 00:00:44,640
How would that work, and how does a planet become a rogue anyway?

8
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:48,420
